</h2>
<center><p>Une fois la departement clique sur cette button, chaque etudiant va avoir la filiere qui il merite.<br /> Notons bien que apres avoir attribuer les filieres aucun etudiant peut s'authentifier</p><br /><div class="btn" style="background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #11273F, #061323, #204773);"><a style="text-decoration:none;color:white"  href='@Url.Action("Attribution","Departement")'>Attribuer</a></div></center>

<div class="content">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" style="background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #11273F, #061323, #204773);">
                        <h4 class="card-title" style="color:white;">Informatique</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body table-responsive">


                        
                        <table class="table table-hover">
                            <thead style="color:#B49082;">
                            <th style="font-weight:bold;">Cne</th>
                            <th style="font-weight:bold;">Cin</th>
                            <th style="font-weight:bold;">Nom</th>
                            <th style="font-weight:bold;">Prenom</th>
                            <th style="font-weight:bold;">Note generale</th>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                @if (Model == null)
                                {

                                }
                                else
                                {

                                    foreach (var item in Model)
                                    {
                                        if (item.idFil == 1)
                                        {
                                            <tr>
                                                <th>
                                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.cne)
                                                </th>
                                                <th>
                                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.cin)
                                                </th>
                                                <td>
                                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.nom)
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.prenom)
                                                </td>

                                                <th>
                                                    @((item.noteSndYear + item.noteFstYear) / 2)
                                                </th>


                                            </tr>
                                        }

                                    }

                                }

                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
